title: The Sun
english_narration: The sun gives us light and warmth every day.

title: The Moon
english_narration: The moon shines bright in the night sky.

title: The Earth
english_narration: The Earth is our home. It has land, water, and air.

title: Trees
english_narration: Trees give us oxygen and make the air fresh.

title: Rain
english_narration: Rain helps plants grow and fills our rivers and ponds.

title: Animals
english_narration: Animals are our friends. They help us in many ways.

title: Birds
english_narration: Birds can fly high in the sky with their wings.

title: Fish
english_narration: Fish live in water and breathe through their gills.

title: Fire
english_narration: Fire gives us heat but can be dangerous too.

title: Milk
english_narration: Cows give us milk, which makes our bones strong.

title: Food
english_narration: We eat food to get energy and stay healthy.
